name: Bmx Girl Wheelie Racing
description:
Download BMX GIRL WHEELIE RACING For Free!!!

Think you are up for this challenge?

The aim here is to finish the level as fast as possible with one wheel.

See how quickly you can do it and perform some fantastic wheelie stunts on the way!

There is no time limit with this game; you can ride at your own pace - but fast and furious is much more fun!
